videos.headline: Duke recovers Bama fumble
videos.description: Alabama RB Jerome Ford loses the football and it is recovered by Duke's Tre Hornbuckle.

videos.headline: Tua connects with his TE to give Bama an early lead
videos.description: Tua Tagovailoa finds TE Miller Forristall down the middle who turns it into a 27-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Tua connects with his TE to give Bama an early lead) 2019/08/31

videos.headline: Robinson extends Bama's lead with short TD
videos.description: Alabama RB Brian Robinson Jr. walks into the end zone giving Alabama the 14-0 lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Robinson extends Bama's lead with short TD) 2019/08/31

videos.headline: Duke WR makes impressive catch late in the first half
videos.description: Duke wide receiver Scott Bracey goes up and hauls in the catch for a 37-yard gain.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Duke WR makes impressive catch late in the first half) 2019/08/31

videos.headline: Duke's Cerenord ejected after incident with Bama offensive lineman
videos.description: Duke defensive lineman Edgar Cerenord is ejected after he gets into it with an Alabama offensive lineman.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_ One-Play (Duke's Cerenord ejected after incident with Bama offensive lineman) 2019/08/31

videos.headline: Tua finds Smith for 10-yard TD
videos.description: Tua Tagovailoa rolls to his right then finds DeVonta Smith, who walks into the end zone for a 10-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Jeudy goes airborne on TD run
videos.description: Jerry Jeudy catches the short pass and shows off his skills for a 21-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Jeudy goes airborne on TD run) 2019/08/31

videos.headline: Tua's brother hands it off to Ford for long TD
videos.description: Tua's brother, Taulia Tagovailoa, hands it off to Jerome Ford who goes 37 yards for the touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Tua's brother hands it off to Ford for long TD) 2019/08/31

videos.headline: Tua racks up 4 TDs in Bama's Week 1 win
videos.description: Tua Tagovailoa throws for 336 yards and four touchdowns to help Alabama dominate Duke 42-3.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Tua racks up 4 TDs in Bama’s Week 1 win ) 2019/08/31 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Jeudy stakes claim as nation's best player
videos.description: After being anointed Mel Kiper's No. 1 NFL draft prospect for 2020, Jerry Jeudy puts on a 10-catch clinic and scores in Alabama's season-opening win.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Jeudy stakes claim as nation’s best player) 2019/08/31 ESHEET ENHL
